The paper deals with multi-objective optimization in a distributed setting, which involves cooperation and learning among agents. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of Multiagent Systems (cs.MA), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Control Systems (cs.SY), or Game Theory (cs.GT). The use of diffusion strategies and gradient descent operators further supports the likelihood of these categories.
